PN,41202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772697873
OL,3,CAnne Boleyn's 'extraordinary' chair on
OL,4,Cdisplay for first time at childhood
OL,5,Chome
OL,7,FAntiques specialist Paul Fitzsimmons
OL,8,Fand Tudor expert Sandra Vasoli have
OL,9,Fbeen leading the research into the
OL,10,Fchair's background.
OL,12,FThey believe the early 16th century
OL,13,Fpiece was intended for Anne while she
OL,14,Fserved Queen Claude of France.
OL,16,FCarvings on the chair include a Tudor
OL,17,Frose bound by the tails of dolphins
OL,18,Fand it features a variety of personal,
OL,19,Fpolitical and ceremonial symbols.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
