PN,41203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772697873
OL,3,CAnne Boleyn's 'extraordinary' chair on
OL,4,Cdisplay for first time at childhood
OL,5,Chome
OL,7,FThe Boleyn family moved to Hever
OL,8,FCastle in around 1505 and Anne lived
OL,9,Fthere until 1513, when she moved to
OL,10,FMechelen in modern-day Belgium.
OL,12,FAnne became an attendant to Queen
OL,13,FClaude the following year.
OL,15,FThe exhibition at Hever, which runs
OL,16,Funtil 2 January 2027, also features
OL,17,Fmany other objects that give an
OL,18,Finsight into Anne's life, including a
OL,19,FCrowned Falcon Badge and a Crowned
OL,20,FLeopard's Head.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
