PN,41204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772697873
OL,3,CAnne Boleyn's 'extraordinary' chair on
OL,4,Cdisplay for first time at childhood
OL,5,Chome
OL,7,FDiscussing the chair, Sandra Vasoli
OL,8,Fsaid: "From the AB monogram to the
OL,9,Fvarious emblems and icons, we have an
OL,10,Fextraordinary convergence of evidence.
OL,12,F"Together, they signal that this Chair
OL,13,Fwas made for Anne during her obscure
OL,14,Fearly years, well before she achieved
OL,15,Ffame as the second wife of Henry VIII."
OL,26,@pD@GOUwD@gO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/7
