PN,41205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772697873
OL,3,CAnne Boleyn's 'extraordinary' chair on
OL,4,Cdisplay for first time at childhood
OL,5,Chome
OL,7,FPaul Fitzsimmons added: "Historical
OL,8,Ftreasures retain a distinct aura of
OL,9,Ftheir past. It is a privilege to
OL,10,Fpartner with Hever Castle to share
OL,11,Fthese extraordinary Tudor objects with
OL,12,Fthe public.
OL,14,F"To stand before them is to come
OL,15,Fcloser to the tangible reality of Anne
OL,16,FBoleyn's world, and I hope exhibit
OL,17,Fvisitors feel that same sense of
OL,18,Fconnection."
OL,26,@oD@YOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
