PN,41206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772697873
OL,3,CAnne Boleyn's 'extraordinary' chair on
OL,4,Cdisplay for first time at childhood
OL,5,Chome
OL,7,FDr Owen Emmerson, Assistant Curator at
OL,8,FHever Castle, said: "It is incredibly
OL,9,Fspecial to see these three remarkable
OL,10,Fobjects (the chair, the falcon badge
OL,11,Fand the leopard's head) on display at
OL,12,FHever Castle, so generously loaned
OL,13,Ffrom Paul Fitzsimmons' peerless
OL,14,Fcollection.
OL,26,@pD@UOUrD@IpmsD@Wpn
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/7
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,413,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F412A1772697873
OL,3,CAnne Boleyn's 'extraordinary' chair on
OL,4,Cdisplay for first time at childhood
OL,5,Chome
OL,7,F"They allow us to broaden the
OL,8,Fconversation about Anne Boleyn's image
OL,9,Fbeyond painted portraits, showing how
OL,10,Fher identity was expressed through
OL,11,Fcarved wood, heraldic emblems, and
OL,12,Fceremonial objects - through the
OL,13,Fspaces she inhabited and the symbols
OL,14,Fshe chose as Queen."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/7
